      "name": [
        "SCAMPER"
      ],
      "description": [
        "<p>Using SCAMPER can help you define possible new products. Many of the ideas may be impractical or may not suit the equipment used by the manufacturer. However some ideas could be good starting points for new products. You can use these changes either as direct suggestions or as starting points for lateral thinking.<\/p>"
      ],
